  "title": "Beautician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To provide professional treatment and beauty consultations</li>\n  <li>Consult and provide treatment advisory</li>\n  <li>To build and maintain good relationship with customers</li>\n  <li>To provide excellent and follow-up services towards customers</li>\n  <li>Attend to enquiries and make appointments</li>\n  <li>Ensure the highest standard of sanitation, exercise good hygiene and ensure tidiness for a safe and pleasant experience for customers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must be able to work in a team and have good interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Keen to learn new things and new trends</li>\n  <li>Experienced beauticians only</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends and Public holidays (retail shifts)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Joining Award for Singapore citizens &amp; Permanent Residents</li>\n  <li>Extra incentives given for sales and service quality</li>\n  <li>Flexible work hours available</li>\n  <li>One of the highest commission in Singapore</li>\n  <li>Career Progression</li>\n</ul>",
